<html><head></head><body dir=3D"auto" style=3D"overflow-wrap: =
break-word; -webkit-nbsp-mode: space; line-break: =
after-white-space;"><div><p data-start=3D"242" data-end=3D"252">Hi =
Zach,</p><p data-start=3D"254" data-end=3D"511">I refer to my Privacy =
Act 2020 requests for full copies of the claim files for C90306048 and =
C90306256, including all internal notes, reports, third-party =
correspondence, scopes, assessments, emails, phone records, texts, and =
any other relevant materials.</p><p data-start=3D"513" =
data-end=3D"923">Despite my request of 1 July 2025, and my reminder to =
Grant on 27 August 2025, I have not yet received any material. Your =
reference to a 25 July 2025 email or communications is unclear, so could =
you kindly resend that correspondence so I have a complete record. =
Please provide the full claim files by 5:00 pm, Monday 1 September 2025, =
as the 20-working-day timeframe under the Privacy Act has already =
passed.</p><p data-start=3D"925" data-end=3D"1296">For ongoing =
compliance, I would also appreciate monthly updates, provided on the 1st =
of each month, of the full and up-to-date files. If providing full =
copies each month is difficult, then per Information Privacy Principle =
6, I am happy to receive monthly summaries of all new additions, with =
the complete file supplied whenever an assessment is submitted or =
presented.</p><p data-start=3D"1298" data-end=3D"1752">In relation to =
the contents claim, to date I have only received a partial list from =
David, which does not include item values, repair or cleaning details, =
or assessment of property outside the house, including under-deck stairs =
and deck items, many of which were significantly affected by heat and =
smoke. As more than three months have now passed without a complete =
schedule or proper assessment, I would be grateful for an urgent update =
on this claim.</p><p data-start=3D"1754" data-end=3D"2110">In relation =
to the house claim, I look forward to receiving the comprehensive update =
from Grant as he indicated. As per his request, I am also happy to meet =
on site, and I can make myself available on Monday at 4:00 pm, Tuesday =
at either 8:00 am or 4:00 pm, Wednesday after 3:30 pm, or Thursday =
before 3:00 pm. Please confirm whichever option works best.</p><p =
data-start=3D"2112" data-end=3D"2273">I trust these matters can be =
resolved promptly. Progress on both claims has been slower than =
expected, which is concerning in light of the Code=E2=80=99s =
requirements.</p><p data-start=3D"2275" data-end=3D"2302">Kind =
regards,<br data-start=3D"2288" data-end=3D"2291">Raffaella</p></div><br =
class=3D"Apple-interchange-newline"><div><div =
class=3D"AppleOriginalContents" style=3D"direction: ltr;"><blockquote =
